## 🚀 Key Features

### 1. Temporal Fusion Transformer
State-of-the-art TFT architecture with **multi-head temporal self-attention** — learns which time steps and features matter most for each SKU, automatically.

### 2. 150+ Engineered Features
Rich feature set including lag features, rolling statistics, Fourier transforms for seasonality, external signals (weather, macro, social), and promotional calendar embeddings.

### 3. Automated HPO with Optuna
Hyperparameter search across architecture depth, learning rate, attention heads, and dropout — reduced tuning time from **3 weeks to 18 hours** using GCP Vertex AI parallel trials.

### 4. Real-Time 4-Hour Refresh
Apache Spark Structured Streaming ingests new transactions continuously; Airflow DAGs trigger model re-inference every 4 hours — keeping forecasts fresh with **zero downtime**.

### 5. Full Observability
Grafana dashboards with rolling MAPE, inventory coverage, and data drift metrics. Automated alerts fire when forecast accuracy degrades beyond threshold.

