## 🛠️ Setup & Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/jaswanth-allam/tft-demandiq-forecasting.git
cd tft-demandiq-forecasting

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure GCP credentials
gcloud auth application-default login

# Run feature pipeline locally (requires Spark)
spark-submit data/spark_streaming_pipeline.py

# Train the TFT model
python training/train_pipeline.py --config models/tft/tft_config.yaml

# Run HPO (optional, requires GCP Vertex AI)
python hpo/optuna_study.py --n-trials 100

# Start the prediction API
uvicorn serving.forecast_api:app --reload --port 8000

# View forecasts in notebook
jupyter notebook notebooks/04_results_analysis.ipynb
```

